QUICK START:
1. Extract: tar -xzf droplet-10-upgrade-v2.0.tar.gz
2. Setup: cp .env.example .env
3. Edit .env:
   - Set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY (required!)
   - Set DROPLET_URL (your public URL)
   - Set DATABASE_URL (or use Docker default)
4. Launch: docker-compose up -d
5. Verify: curl http://localhost:8000/health
6. Dashboard: http://localhost:3000

